    title: "Studio 823",
    role: "Architect",
    company: "Studio Eight Twentythree",
    dates: "2018 - 2021",
    location: "Mumbai, India",
    desc: "Architect at Studio Eight Twentythree: Began as an intern during my final year of architecture studies and transitioned into a full-time role post-graduation. Contributed to diverse projects across hospitality, commercial spaces, architectural research, and residential interior design. Mentored by Samir Raut and Faizan Khatri, I honed my skills in a dynamic, enriching environment that laid the foundation for my professional growth. (Full Time)"
